channel.title: Dofus
channel.description: Well, theres this MMORPG I've been playing for a few years called DOFUS and thought I shoudl share it with you guys. It's very similar to Final Fantasy Tactics if you've ever played it and pretty addicting. Theres this thing going on called Godfather Fortunes that if you get enough people to click your link and register you get prizes and stuff. Registration link: https://www.dofus.com/en/godfather-fortunes-account-creation/andrewross22
